String

length -- strlen()

count no of words -- str_word_count()

Reverse a string -- strrev()

search for text -- strpos("words", "text")  output will be position of text

Replace a string -- str_replace("wat to Replace", "replacer", "text" )

compare 2 strings -- strcmp()



Date Time

To check date -- Checkdate()
Add date and others -- date_add()


Array

crate array -- array()
change all case in key -- array_change_key_case()
split array into chunks -- array_chunk()
fill array with values -- array_fill()
exchange all keys to values -- array_flip()
check if a key exist -- array_key_exists()
merge arrays -- array_merge()
insert a specified no of items with values -- array_pad()
calculate product of values -- array_product()
insert elements to end of array -- array_push()
Replace elements of first array -- array_replace()
reverse array -- array_reverse()
search for value and return key -- array_search()
remove duplicate value of array -- array_unique()
sort associative array according to ascending value -- asort()
sort associative array according to descending value -- arsort()
sort associative array according to ascending key -- ksort()
sort associative array according to descending key -- krsort()
count elements in an array -- count()
creates array containing range of elements -- range()
sort indexed array in ascending order -- sort()
sort indexed array in descending order -- rsort()
sort an array in natural order -- natsort()
change pointer know position and reset to first pointer -- next(), prev(), pos(), reset()
shuffle an array -- shuffle()
